{
  "id": "adv_event_2502_01_05",
  "title": "あなたに\nハッピー\nバレンタイン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "企画コーナー、凄く盛り上がった……\n楽しいイベントもいよいよ大詰め……次が最後の曲……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The special segment was a huge hit…\nThis fun event is finally reaching its finale… the next song is the last one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.8968254089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.0871168822
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0834919612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "最後に歌うのは、私達が作ったバレンタインの曲です\n恋愛ソングなんて、ちょっと恥ずかしいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final song is a Valentine’s song that we made ourselves.\nA love song is a little embarrassing‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0834919612,
      "endTime": 18.422283617799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6156168938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピらしい恋愛ソングってどんな曲だろうって\nみんなで一杯考えて、話し合いながら作ったんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We kept wondering what a “Sunny Peace–style” love song would be like‚\nand made it together through lots of discussions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6156168938,
      "endTime": 26.4632357599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6565690359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと恋の話をするのが新鮮で、楽しくて、おかげで\nドキドキワクワクする私達らしい恋の歌が出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about love with everyone felt fresh and fun‚\nand thanks to that‚ we created a heart-pounding‚ exciting love song that really feels like us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6565690359,
      "endTime": 36.6069548926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.8202879589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "楽しくて幸せな、サニーピースのバレンタインチョコ\nどうぞ召し上がれ――『ラブリー♡♡♡♡♡♡』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fun and happy Sunny Peace Valentine’s chocolate—\nplease enjoy it—“Lovely ♡♡♡♡♡♡”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8202879589,
      "endTime": 45.6513310117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.2856388093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインイベント終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the Valentine’s event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5246625266,
      "endTime": 48.0246602378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0246602378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなお疲れ様。バレンタインらしい愛に溢れた\n素敵なステージだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great work‚ everyone. It was a stage overflowing\nwith Valentine’s-style love—truly wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8579930625,
      "endTime": 54.433333333300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.675045554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n私達もお客さんの声援から沢山の愛をもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nWe received so much love from the audience’s cheers as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.675045554,
      "endTime": 61.7766765278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.9833429655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンも、私達も、みんな幸せ……\nバレンタインイベント、やって良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans‚ us… everyone is happy…\nI’m glad we did this Valentine’s event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9833429655,
      "endTime": 69.7026172955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなが誰に本命チョコを渡したのか気になるが……）\n（今の幸せそうな彼女達に、水を差すなんて出来ないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m curious about who everyone gave their true feeling Valentine chocolate to‚ but…）\n（I can’t spoil their happiness right now.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8959506671,
      "endTime": 79.4906446139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6773110707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（余計な詮索はやめておこう。みんなが幸せなら、俺は）\n（どんな相手だろうと受け入れ……受け入れ……ぐぬぬ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I should stop prying. As long as they’re happy‚）\n（I’ll accept it no matter who it is… accept it… ngh…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6773110707,
      "endTime": 92.1744765599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、{user}君。今夜チョコを\n寮に持って来る約束ちゃんと覚えてるわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}. You remember your promise\nto bring the chocolates to the dorm tonight‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3611430168,
      "endTime": 98.7505533218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9505534172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "大事な話があるので、忘れずに来て下さいね\n待ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have something important to talk about‚\nso please don’t forget. We’ll be waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9505534172,
      "endTime": 104.1666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4381365935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（大事な話？　まさか、みんなの好きな人を……）\n（恋人を俺に打ち明けるつもりなのか！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something important? Don’t tell me…）\n（Are they about to tell me who they love… their partners!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4381365935,
      "endTime": 114.0874789397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3008122921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（私生活には口出ししないようにしていたが）\n（サニピ全員に恋人がいたなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ve avoided interfering in their private lives‚ but…）\n（If every Sunny Peace member has a partner…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3008122921,
      "endTime": 120.921719408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.1283860366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（一体いつからこんなことに……）\n（これが世間に知られたら大変なことになるぞ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Since when did this happen…）\n（If the public finds out‚ it’ll be a disaster!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1283860366,
      "endTime": 127.73162872009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9382953485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？\nどうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?\nIs something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9382953485,
      "endTime": 131.4999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……いや、なんでもない……\n俺なら大丈夫だ。しっかり寮までチョコを届けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… no‚ it’s nothing…\nI’m fine. I’ll make sure to bring the chocolates to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7637146951,
      "endTime": 139.3278872491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.5145540875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（落ち着け、みんなは俺を信頼して話すつもりなんだ）\n（だったら俺も、みんなの信頼に応えないと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Calm down. They’re planning to talk because they trust me.）\n（Then I need to live up to that trust!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5145540875,
      "endTime": 149.5555742901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.742241033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……しっかり俺も心の準備をして行くよ\nみんながどんな決断をしようとちゃんと受け止めるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll prepare myself mentally before I go.\nNo matter what decisions you’ve made‚ I’ll accept them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.742241033,
      "endTime": 160.8922414145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.6333315532
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.105574767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "だから信じてほしい……\n何があっても、俺はみんなの味方だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please trust me…\nNo matter what happens‚ I’m on your side!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.105574767,
      "endTime": 167.5026497525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Later that night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.5159830095,
      "endTime": 169.706593196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "事務所に届いていたチョコを全部持って来たから\n自分の分は部屋に運んでおいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought all the chocolates that arrived at the office‚\nso take your own portions to your rooms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6159855527,
      "endTime": 176.6623572988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、俺に大事な話があるんだよな？\n覚悟は出来ている。みんなの話を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ you had something important to tell me‚ right?\nI’m ready. Let me hear what you have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8756904604,
      "endTime": 185.9346702578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、勇気を出して打ち明けますね\n{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I’ll gather my courage and tell you.\n{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.1280033431,
      "endTime": 195.7445081398,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12671.996656900006
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもありがとうございます！\nこれ、私達の気持ちです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for everything‚ always!\nThis is how we feel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.0264324507,
      "endTime": 200.8658883414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは、もしかして……\n……バレンタインのチョコレート？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this is… could it be…\n…Valentine’s chocolate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.0592215699,
      "endTime": 208.52913104700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　みんなで手作りしたんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We all made it together by hand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.7357977709,
      "endTime": 212.0635301432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "鳩が豆鉄砲を食らったような顔をしてるわね\nそんなに意外だったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look like a pigeon that just got hit with a pea shooter.\nWas it really that surprising?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.2768634957,
      "endTime": 218.728541581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズ大成功……ぶい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprise was a huge success… V!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.9152082285,
      "endTime": 222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "手作りのチョコを俺に？　そうだったのか……\n自分がもらうなんて全然考えてなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Handmade chocolate… for me? So that’s what it was…\nI never once thought I’d be the one receiving it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.3314791601,
      "endTime": 233.77179707699997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いつもお世話になってるんだから当然です。むしろ\nどうして私達からもらえないと思ったのか聞きたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re always taking care of us‚ so of course. If anything‚\nI want to know why you thought you wouldn’t get anything from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.9717971724,
      "endTime": 241.9239969177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
