      "text": "……もしかして、迷惑でしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Was it a bother?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.1373299839,
      "endTime": 245.4845175507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、ある訳ないだろ。凄く嬉しいよ\nみんな、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way. I’m incredibly happy.\nThank you‚ everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.6845176461,
      "endTime": 254.3499828102,
      "sfxList": []
