      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうを言うのは……\n感謝を伝えるのは私達の方です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ones who should be saying thank you…\nthe ones who should be sharing gratitude are us.",
        "id": ""
