      "text": "大変なことも沢山あったけど\nずっとマネージャーで居続けてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were so many hard times‚ but\nthank you for staying our manager all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.5766947034,
      "endTime": 266.590731168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "私達を見つけてくれて……\nアイドルにしてくれて、ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for finding us…\nand for making us idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.7907310727,
      "endTime": 272.71877710850003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "いつもそばにいて、見守ってくれて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for always being by our side\nand watching over us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.9187772992,
      "endTime": 277.86662826549997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei006.m4a",
